<subSubSection id="CBF8B9AF4071EB87DA7C9D4402774CE6" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="252B55B44FD7F52E835F193E17559074" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="52DE5ECF5A451C06E1F19D75EB555AAD" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Mexico (
<normalizedToken id="E6A59BECD0742E2C2A42FF66DF77C6D8" originalValue="Querétaro">Queretaro</normalizedToken>
, Veracruz) in tropical dry forest and cloud forest, including 
<taxonomicName id="4C64A99168AE61005EA0DD2A350B5461" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fagaceae" genus="Quercus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Quercus" order="Fagales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="170CC4420A21A92D52A0E8A709972DE9" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Quercus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="1344BB85B84991E09AB7AA30A9A71540" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Betulaceae" genus="Carpinus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Carpinus" order="Fagales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="D4737C5A5A8554F1CF2DC662858D8E58" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Carpinus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="892A1E6C5C5C608C499D9A03D27C1151" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Altingiaceae" genus="Liquidambar" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Liquidambar" order="Saxifragales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5D019D29B0E9FCDFC41588F148B201AB" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Liquidambar</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
forest, in shady canyons and on slopes, sometimes on limestone, 1040-1450 m in elevation (Fig. 
<figureCitation id="397168F0A3F581D36BCE50AE629F5A25" captionStart="Figure 41" captionStartId="F41" captionText="Figure 41. Map of geographic distribution of L. glabripetala based on herbarium specimen data." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.168.51904.figure41" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/480053" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">41</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption id="1A458C2547D94EAE53B4018A96AFC88A" doi="10.3897/phytokeys.168.51904.figure41" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/480053" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" start="Figure 41" startId="F41">
